&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Are you a veteran of hardware program management who thrives where physical hardware meets high-stakes operational environments? Have you managed complex new product introductions (NPI) or scaled infrastructure solutions across commercial business footprints?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
